OL,3,CGrandmother 'cried all night' after
OL,4,Cpet dog was killed by a cyclist
OL,6,FA grandmother from Cheltenham who says
OL,7,Fher pet dog is the "love of her life"
OL,8,Fhas been left heartbroken after she
OL,9,Fwas killed by a cyclist.
OL,11,FShirley Harvey was walking Lady in
OL,12,FBurrows Playing Field in Leckhampton
OL,13,Fwhen the chihuahua was struck on
OL,14,FSaturday 30 March.
OL,16,FThe 79-year-old said she was "crying
OL,17,Fall night" after watching her dog die.
OL,19,FShirley said: "I loved her and she
OL,20,Floved me and it's very hard to accept
OL,21,Fwhat happened. She did nothing wrong.
