OL,3,CGrandmother 'cried all night' after
OL,4,Cpet dog was killed by a cyclist
OL,6,F"I took her for a walk that morning
OL,7,Fover the park just across the road. We
OL,8,Ftook her lead off and she was just
OL,9,Fsniffing about in the grass and not on
OL,10,Fthe lead and a man came down on a tiny
OL,11,Flittle bike.
OL,13,F"I said 'watch the dog' and the next
OL,14,Fminute he ran straight over her body
OL,15,Fand I heard this terrific scream.
OL,17,F"I carried her home and she was still
OL,18,Fwarm and cuddly and I was screaming.
