OL,3,CGrandmother 'cried all night' after
OL,4,Cpet dog was killed by a cyclist
OL,6,F"I called my son who came over
OL,7,Fstraight away and he said 'mum, she's
OL,8,Fgone.'
OL,10,F"He said 'mum, you've got to leave her
OL,11,Fnow. Let her rest.
OL,13,F"I lay awake all night just crying and
OL,14,FI've been so upset ever since.
OL,16,F"I'll never forget that scream."
OL,18,FThe 79-year-old's husband died five
OL,19,Fyears ago and was given the dog by her
OL,20,Fgranddaughter to help her through her
OL,21,Fgrief.
