OL,3,CGrandmother 'cried all night' after
OL,4,Cpet dog was killed by a cyclist
OL,6,FShirley said: "My husband died five
OL,7,Fyears ago so I was given Lady by my
OL,8,Fgranddaughter and it turned my life
OL,9,Faround.
OL,11,F"I was with her 24 hours a day, she
OL,12,Fused to sleep on my bed, she was very
OL,13,Fcuddly and very sweet."
OL,15,FGloucestershire Police are trying to
OL,16,Ftrace a man described as being heavy
OL,17,Fand wearing a black cycle helmet while
OL,18,Friding a small bike.
OL,20,FThe force is keen to talk to a woman
OL,21,Fwho witnessed the incident.
